snippet.title: Freshly Frosted Launch Trailer | Releasing Soon!
snippet.description:
Solve puzzles in the world's most adorable donut factory!

A dozen dozen dazzling donut dilemmas await you in Freshly Frosted, a wholesome puzzle game that takes place in the world's most adorable donut factory. Place conveyor belts to guide these sweet treats through frosting and sprinkle machines to the delivery counter. With 144 puzzles, 12 different donut shapes, a comforting and encouraging narrative, and a number of unique mechanics, you're sure to find something you enjoy!

Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1070790/Freshly_Frosted/
